arStrings.szText:
After moving {c_number}{SF_0}{/c} meters, your next {c_important}Core{/c} or {c_important}Ultimate{/c} Skill deals {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|%x|]{/c} increased damage. 

While this damage bonus is ready, your {c_important}Basic{/c}, {c_important}Agility{/c}, and {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skills deal {c_number}[{SF_3}*100|%x|]{/c} increased damage.
Your next Core or Ultimate attack deals increased damage. Agility and Subterfuge Skills are dealing more damage.
